15 વષઁ ની મંજરી— Blossom, Florescence

Manjhari, like her name, was a new wave of blossom. But just like everything else, Manjhari had a secret side Inside of her, there used to be a youthful, joyful, carefree girl as well, before she became that mature, stubborn, fearless woman.
Even though this sequence wasn't in the film, it still holds a very special place in my heart. This scene provides insight into Manjari's early life. Her personality did not always exist from childhood; rather, it emerged through time. Like all young girls, Manjhari had moon and star-filled dreams. She wanted to live the way her heart desires.
